#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.zfill.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.zfill"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:1
msgid "Pad strings in the Series/Index by prepending '0' characters."
msgstr "通过在字符串前面添加 '0' 字符来填充 Series/Index 中的字符串。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:3
msgid ""
"Strings in the Series/Index are padded with '0' characters on the left of"
" the string to reach a total string length  `width`. Strings in the "
"Series/Index with length greater or equal to `width` are unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Series/Index 中的字符串会在左侧添加 '0' 字符，使其总长度达到 `width`。"
"长度大于或等于 `width` 的字符串将保持不变。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:8
msgid ""
"Minimum length of resulting string; strings with length less than `width`"
" be prepended with '0' characters."
msgstr "结果字符串的最小长度；长度小于 `width` 的字符串将在前面添加 '0' 字符。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:16
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.rjust`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:17
msgid "Fills the left side of strings with an arbitrary character."
msgstr "用任意字符填充字符串的左侧。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:19
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.ljust`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:20
msgid "Fills the right side of strings with an arbitrary character."
msgstr "用任意字符填充字符串的右侧。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:22
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.pad`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:23
msgid "Fills the specified sides of strings with an arbitrary character."
msgstr "用任意字符填充字符串的指定侧。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:25
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.center`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:26
msgid "Fills both sides of strings with an arbitrary character."
msgstr "用任意字符填充字符串的两侧。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:29
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:30
msgid ""
"Differs from :meth:`str.zfill` which has special handling for '+'/'-' in "
"the string."
msgstr "与 :meth:`str.zfill` 不同，后者对字符串中的 '+'/'-' 有特殊处理。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:34
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.zfill:46
msgid ""
"Note that ``10`` and ``NaN`` are not strings, therefore they are "
"converted to ``NaN``. The minus sign in ``'-1'`` is treated as a special "
"character and the zero is added to the right of it (:meth:`str.zfill` "
"would have moved it to the left). ``1000`` remains unchanged as it is "
"longer than `width`."
msgstr ""
"注意 ``10`` 和 ``NaN`` 不是字符串，因此它们会被转换为 ``NaN``。``'-1'`` "
"中的负号被视为特殊字符，零被添加到它的右侧（:meth:`str.zfill` 会将其移到"
"左侧）。``1000`` 保持不变，因为它的长度超过了 `width`。"

